data.description: !PRICE DROP! SELLER MOTIVATED! Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the coveted Sandy Oaks neighborhood. Its white vinyl fencing adds elegance and security. Inside, enjoy an open layout, and the upgraded garage with custom cabinets and a workstation. Home features All updated appliances as well as newer A/C unit installed for peace of mind. The spacious backyard invites outdoor activities. Conveniently located and ready for you to see, don't miss the chance to make it yours!
